

裝mysql
sudo apt-get install mysql-server
sudo apt-get install php5-mysql

初使化資料庫
	cd database
	cat *.sql | mysql -u root -p

database sign in information setting
	modify appendectomy/config/database.php
	
	$db['default']['username'] = 'your database username';
	$db['default']['password'] = 'your pass word';
	$db['default']['database'] = 'your database name'; //default is appendectomy

看資料庫
	http://www.phpmyadmin.net/home_page/downloads.php
	
codeigniter
	http://www.codeigniter.org.tw/downloads
	
主要程式
	application / controllers / appy.php
	說明文件：
		http://www.codeigniter.org.tw/user_guide/database/active_record.html
		http://www.codeigniter.org.tw/user_guide/database/results.html